00:00:29,605 --> 00:00:35,765
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

2
00:01:55,885 --> 00:01:58,685
EPISODE 11

3
00:02:03,525 --> 00:02:05,205
Ugly like me?

4
00:02:08,245 --> 00:02:12,005
Don't you have anything nice to say to me?

5
00:02:24,045 --> 00:02:24,885
Fangfang.

6
00:02:24,965 --> 00:02:26,565
What are you looking at?

7
00:02:27,765 --> 00:02:28,645
Fangfang.

8
00:02:37,565 --> 00:02:39,885
Zhang Fangfang.

9
00:02:41,245 --> 00:02:43,205
-What is it?
-What are you looking at?

10
00:02:44,765 --> 00:02:45,605
Nothing.

11
00:02:47,965 --> 00:02:49,205
If I'm not mistaken,

12
00:02:49,685 --> 00:02:52,045
this is a man's jacket.

13
00:02:53,605 --> 00:02:55,685
Come on, don't be shy. Just say it.

14
00:02:55,765 --> 00:02:56,845
No, it's nothing.

15
00:02:58,165 --> 00:02:59,205
We have class tomorrow.

16
00:02:59,645 --> 00:03:00,645
You should go to bed now.

17
00:03:00,725 --> 00:03:02,205
Fangfang, you're blushing.

18
00:03:15,125 --> 00:03:16,965
-Hey, Qingqing!
-Yes?

19
00:03:17,165 --> 00:03:19,405
The bonsai I gave you yesterday,
don't water it too much.

20
00:03:21,045 --> 00:03:22,165
Goodness.

21
00:03:22,685 --> 00:03:24,885
You should take care of yourself first.

22
00:03:25,045 --> 00:03:26,925
Can't you be a little nicer?

23
00:03:28,045 --> 00:03:31,125
Sometimes, you're quite interesting.

24
00:03:31,445 --> 00:03:33,885
You can do quite a lot.

25
00:03:34,005 --> 00:03:36,045
Can you just stop pulling that scary face?

26
00:03:36,725 --> 00:03:39,125
You're the scaredy-cat here, Feng.

27
00:03:40,125 --> 00:03:43,325
When I'm a little nicer, you like me.

28
00:03:43,405 --> 00:03:46,205
But when I'm a little rude,
you chicken out right away!

29
00:03:47,365 --> 00:03:49,405
Hey, since when do I like you?

30
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:55,165
I mean

31
00:03:55,725 --> 00:03:58,605
who gave you the idea to determine
what girls should be like?

32
00:03:59,045 --> 00:04:00,685
If we want to define ourselves,

33
00:04:00,765 --> 00:04:03,045
we've got to be modest and gentle
to everyone else.

34
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:04,965
What era are we in now?

35
00:04:05,045 --> 00:04:06,925
Actually, that's not what I meant either.

36
00:04:07,405 --> 00:04:09,725
You just need half
of Qingchen's qualities.

37
00:04:12,565 --> 00:04:14,605
Let me ask you this.

38
00:04:14,685 --> 00:04:17,685
Do you know what Qingchen is like?

39
00:04:17,765 --> 00:04:21,365
I see that she has a special place
in your heart.

40
00:04:21,445 --> 00:04:23,885
She's the lead actress of my music video.

41
00:04:24,325 --> 00:04:27,285
Not only she's gorgeous and polite,

42
00:04:27,365 --> 00:04:28,845
but she's also approachable.

43
00:04:29,405 --> 00:04:31,685
You should get to know her
when you get the chance.

44
00:04:31,765 --> 00:04:34,485
You've got a lot to learn from her
to improve yourself.

45
00:04:34,565 --> 00:04:36,245
Right, Gu Nanxi?

46
00:04:36,325 --> 00:04:37,245
Yes.

47
00:04:37,685 --> 00:04:38,925
And she's beautiful.

48
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:43,405
Her fingers were dancing on the piano keys

49
00:04:44,405 --> 00:04:45,485
just like fairies.

50
00:04:46,885 --> 00:04:49,525
Musical fairies.

51
00:04:51,285 --> 00:04:53,845
Hey! You two rich kids.

52
00:04:54,245 --> 00:04:57,245
Now, I really want to buy a huge mirror

53
00:04:57,325 --> 00:05:00,485
so I can show you
what you really look like.

54
00:05:02,285 --> 00:05:03,525
I want to ask the both of you.

55
00:05:04,565 --> 00:05:09,045
Don't you notice anything strange

56
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:10,525
about this Qingchen?

57
00:05:11,085 --> 00:05:13,605
She always shows up with a "bang"!

58
00:05:14,965 --> 00:05:16,685
Right in front of you.

59
00:05:16,765 --> 00:05:20,605
Then she goes "bang" again and disappears.

60
00:05:21,165 --> 00:05:23,245
Comes without a shadow,
goes without a trace.

61
00:05:23,805 --> 00:05:24,765
There's more.

62
00:05:25,245 --> 00:05:30,085
Doesn't she always wear a very long dress

63
00:05:30,645 --> 00:05:34,965
every time you meet her?

64
00:05:35,965 --> 00:05:39,405
That's because she has no feet.

65
00:05:40,685 --> 00:05:41,725
And no shadow.

66
00:05:43,805 --> 00:05:45,565
Good point.

67
00:05:46,685 --> 00:05:49,365
Every time I try to call her,
I couldn't get through.

68
00:05:50,125 --> 00:05:52,085
And sometimes,
the number is out of service.

69
00:05:53,725 --> 00:05:54,805
You'd only meet her

70
00:05:55,885 --> 00:05:58,965
at a certain time and in a certain place.

71
00:06:00,125 --> 00:06:03,165
Yet it's not so easy to see her.

72
00:06:08,485 --> 00:06:09,485
Don't tell me

73
00:06:10,245 --> 00:06:12,325
that you've been seeing a ghost?

74
00:06:15,565 --> 00:06:16,725
Look over there!

75
00:06:46,685 --> 00:06:49,125
Chen Qingqing, what are you up to?

76
00:07:16,725 --> 00:07:17,765
Fangfang!

77
00:07:17,845 --> 00:07:19,925
Why did I see you with Lin Yiyang?

78
00:07:20,005 --> 00:07:20,845
No.

79
00:07:20,925 --> 00:07:23,365
My clothes got ripped off.
Then he lent me his jacket.

80
00:07:23,445 --> 00:07:25,885
I was just returning it.
There's nothing between us.

81
00:07:25,965 --> 00:07:26,805
Is that so?

82
00:07:27,525 --> 00:07:28,725
Listen, Fangfang.

83
00:07:28,965 --> 00:07:31,565
You've got to stay away from Yiyang
if you don't need his help.

84
00:07:31,645 --> 00:07:33,885
He's not what he seems to be.

85
00:07:34,805 --> 00:07:36,725
Don't worry, I know that.

86
00:07:38,885 --> 00:07:40,285
-Hello, ma'am.
-Hello, ma'am.

87
00:07:42,045 --> 00:07:44,525
Fangfang, go back to the dorm.
I'll see you there in a minute.

88
00:07:44,645 --> 00:07:45,605
Bye.

89
00:07:47,005 --> 00:07:47,965
Hi, Ms. Chen.

90
00:07:48,485 --> 00:07:49,965
-What is it?
-I want to ask you.

91
00:07:50,045 --> 00:07:52,325
Is there a great alumnus in our school

92
00:07:52,405 --> 00:07:53,965
that goes by the name of Xiao Jingnan?

93
00:07:57,125 --> 00:07:58,445
Why do you ask?

94
00:07:59,445 --> 00:08:00,525
It's like this.

95
00:08:00,965 --> 00:08:02,685
The Students Council

96
00:08:02,765 --> 00:08:04,285
is now sorting out the archives

97
00:08:04,365 --> 00:08:06,205
of the school's most notable students.

98
00:08:06,285 --> 00:08:09,405
So I'd like to get to learn more
and get to know him better.

99
00:08:09,485 --> 00:08:11,965
He was indeed an excellent person.

100
00:08:12,045 --> 00:08:12,925
Really?

101
00:08:13,445 --> 00:08:14,725
Do you know him?

102
00:08:16,485 --> 00:08:18,005
His data is at the College Archives.

103
00:08:18,085 --> 00:08:19,445
If you want to know more,

104
00:08:19,525 --> 00:08:20,765
you just have to go there.

105
00:08:20,845 --> 00:08:22,325
Is there anything else?

106
00:08:22,405 --> 00:08:23,485
No.

107
00:08:23,565 --> 00:08:24,525
Thank you, ma'am.

108
00:08:33,284 --> 00:08:35,164
May I have your attention, please?

109
00:08:35,245 --> 00:08:37,765
The candidate list
for the school's play has been announced.

110
00:08:37,845 --> 00:08:40,725
Come and see if you've made the cut
to share the stage with the stars!

111
00:08:41,645 --> 00:08:42,564
Excuse me.

112
00:08:42,645 --> 00:08:43,885
May I take a look?

113
00:08:45,485 --> 00:08:48,164
"Instructed by Chen Xiao?" That means...

114
00:08:49,805 --> 00:08:51,845
This is fantastic.

115
00:08:52,205 --> 00:08:53,285
No way!

116
00:08:53,925 --> 00:08:56,045
Even the witch can't keep her day job?

117
00:08:56,285 --> 00:08:58,325
This is really weird.

118
00:09:00,725 --> 00:09:01,565
Qingqing, look.

119
00:09:01,645 --> 00:09:03,045
You made the cut.

120
00:09:03,125 --> 00:09:04,645
I'm at the top of the list!

121
00:09:04,725 --> 00:09:06,445
They really have good a taste.

122
00:09:07,365 --> 00:09:09,405
This is the list of supporting actors.

123
00:09:09,485 --> 00:09:11,125
The main cast is over there.

124
00:09:11,925 --> 00:09:13,525
It's them again!

125
00:09:25,445 --> 00:09:28,005
Do you think you can be the main actress?

126
00:09:29,005 --> 00:09:31,085
-You'd be a laughing stock.
-Yeah.

127
00:09:31,165 --> 00:09:33,805
This opportunity
is certainly made for Xinya.

128
00:09:33,885 --> 00:09:35,925
You should just stick to being an extra.

129
00:09:36,005 --> 00:09:36,885
Yeah.

130
00:09:38,725 --> 00:09:40,325
You two take a good look at the list.

131
00:09:40,645 --> 00:09:43,405
I don't know how many rungs
your names are below mine.

132
00:09:43,485 --> 00:09:45,365
You didn't even make it as extras.

133
00:09:45,925 --> 00:09:46,765
And as for you...

134
00:09:48,245 --> 00:09:49,125
How do I put it?

135
00:09:49,925 --> 00:09:52,445
I've never seen how well you act.

136
00:09:52,525 --> 00:09:54,045
So you want to see

137
00:09:54,565 --> 00:09:56,445
how well I strut my stuff on stage?

138
00:09:57,925 --> 00:09:59,605
Then I'll just have to wait and see.

139
00:09:59,845 --> 00:10:03,365
But you'd better not let me down!

140
00:10:04,845 --> 00:10:05,845
Bring it on.

141
00:10:06,965 --> 00:10:07,845
Bring it on.

142
00:10:15,725 --> 00:10:16,885
What's wrong, Feng?

143
00:10:19,525 --> 00:10:20,405
First of all,

144
00:10:21,245 --> 00:10:22,965
congratulations for making the cut

145
00:10:23,045 --> 00:10:25,365
into the Beauty and the Beast lineup.

146
00:10:26,725 --> 00:10:28,485
In the next few hours,

147
00:10:28,645 --> 00:10:30,165
I will conduct the drama class

148
00:10:30,245 --> 00:10:31,845
on behalf of Ms. Wang.

149
00:10:32,445 --> 00:10:34,045
And in two weeks,

150
00:10:35,245 --> 00:10:36,805
we will have a performance.

151
00:10:39,885 --> 00:10:42,365
Gu Nanxi, you managed to come up
with a good plan.

152
00:10:42,685 --> 00:10:44,085
You shall be the director.

153
00:10:44,165 --> 00:10:45,605
Yes, ma'am.

154
00:10:49,045 --> 00:10:51,165
Next, we will assign your roles.

155
00:10:51,645 --> 00:10:52,845
Your rehearsal begins now.

156
00:10:53,285 --> 00:10:55,605
In this scene,
Belle trespasses the West Wing

157
00:10:55,685 --> 00:10:56,845
and then she sees a rose.

158
00:10:56,925 --> 00:10:57,965
The Beast drives her away.

159
00:10:58,445 --> 00:11:01,005
CHIP, MRS POTTS, COGSWORTH, LUMIÈRE

160
00:11:01,085 --> 00:11:05,405
Could it be that no one notices my talent?

161
00:11:05,485 --> 00:11:08,005
I don't think
it's just a matter of talent.

162
00:11:10,205 --> 00:11:12,285
COGSWORTH, LUMIÈRE

163
00:11:17,605 --> 00:11:18,725
Feng.

164
00:11:19,045 --> 00:11:21,605
This is my first stage play,
so I don't have any experience.

165
00:11:21,685 --> 00:11:23,765
Can you give me some advice?

166
00:11:24,325 --> 00:11:26,565
Well, Xinya, you're all good.

167
00:11:26,645 --> 00:11:27,645
I believe in you.

168
00:11:32,805 --> 00:11:33,645
All right.

169
00:11:33,805 --> 00:11:34,805
Ready?

170
00:11:34,885 --> 00:11:35,765
Action!

171
00:11:43,685 --> 00:11:45,085
What are you doing?

172
00:11:45,805 --> 00:11:47,005
Did you touch it?

173
00:11:48,485 --> 00:11:49,525
I'm sorry!

174
00:11:49,605 --> 00:11:50,525
Do you realize

175
00:11:51,485 --> 00:11:52,965
that you could have damned us all?

176
00:11:53,045 --> 00:11:55,885
But I didn't mean any harm.

177
00:11:56,725 --> 00:11:57,845
Get out!

178
00:11:58,685 --> 00:12:00,605
I'm sorry!

179
00:12:00,685 --> 00:12:01,525
Get out of here.

180
00:12:02,845 --> 00:12:04,965
Promise or no promise,

181
00:12:05,245 --> 00:12:06,965
I can't stay here another minute!

182
00:12:08,645 --> 00:12:09,885
Cut! Stop!

183
00:12:09,965 --> 00:12:13,165
Nanxi, how did I do? Did I play it well?

184
00:12:13,245 --> 00:12:14,285
Not...

185
00:12:14,525 --> 00:12:15,685
Not too bad.

186
00:12:16,725 --> 00:12:17,605
It's just that

187
00:12:18,405 --> 00:12:20,325
you need to give your movements

188
00:12:20,965 --> 00:12:22,045
a little restraint.

189
00:12:22,125 --> 00:12:23,125
A little restraint?

190
00:12:23,205 --> 00:12:25,525
Because you moved about so much.

191
00:12:25,765 --> 00:12:26,645
We don't need that.

192
00:12:26,725 --> 00:12:27,565
Got it?

193
00:12:29,445 --> 00:12:30,885
Got it. A little restraint.

194
00:12:31,445 --> 00:12:32,965
Okay, let's do it again.

195
00:12:33,045 --> 00:12:34,005
All right.

196
00:12:38,445 --> 00:12:40,445
Take two. Ready?

197
00:12:40,525 --> 00:12:41,765
Action!

198
