00:12:48,085 --> 00:12:49,445
You could have damned us all!

201
00:12:49,525 --> 00:12:52,845
But I didn't mean any harm!

202
00:12:53,245 --> 00:12:54,125
Get out!

203
00:12:56,805 --> 00:12:58,405
Promise or no promise,

204
00:12:58,485 --> 00:13:00,645
I can't stay here another minute!

205
00:13:02,445 --> 00:13:03,485
One more time!

206
00:13:05,045 --> 00:13:06,165
I'm sorry.

207
00:13:06,245 --> 00:13:08,485
I didn't mean any harm.

208
00:13:08,565 --> 00:13:09,445
Get out of here.

209
00:13:12,645 --> 00:13:14,685
-One more time!
-I didn't mean any harm.

210
00:13:14,765 --> 00:13:15,685
Get out!

211
00:13:18,685 --> 00:13:19,685
One more time!

212
00:13:19,765 --> 00:13:22,045
I didn't mean any harm.

213
00:13:22,765 --> 00:13:23,765
Get out!

214
00:13:26,845 --> 00:13:28,645
Promise or no promise,

215
00:13:28,725 --> 00:13:30,805
I can't stay here another minute!

216
00:13:55,885 --> 00:13:56,765
Ms. Chen.

217
00:13:57,525 --> 00:13:58,805
Can I be frank with you?

218
00:13:59,365 --> 00:14:01,325
-Go ahead.
-I think that

219
00:14:01,405 --> 00:14:04,405
if we want to improve the quality
of the play,

220
00:14:04,805 --> 00:14:08,085
I think the role of Belle should go to

221
00:14:09,005 --> 00:14:10,245
Situ Feng!

222
00:14:12,005 --> 00:14:12,885
Qingqing.

223
00:14:13,125 --> 00:14:14,885
You shouldn't joke around all the time.

224
00:14:15,445 --> 00:14:17,765
Ms. Chen, I'm not joking at all.

225
00:14:17,845 --> 00:14:19,205
Gu Nanxi can prove it.

226
00:14:19,565 --> 00:14:21,285
Situ Feng's women's clothes

227
00:14:21,365 --> 00:14:24,045
are really nice.

228
00:14:25,005 --> 00:14:26,685
Yes, they are.

229
00:14:27,325 --> 00:14:28,285
Gu Nanxi!

230
00:14:31,125 --> 00:14:33,085
Are you both pulling a prank on me?

231
00:14:33,645 --> 00:14:36,125
Goodness, seriously.

232
00:14:36,365 --> 00:14:39,525
What I said is all true.

233
00:14:39,605 --> 00:14:42,205
We're praising you,
so don't give me that look.

234
00:14:43,085 --> 00:14:44,205
All right.

235
00:14:45,125 --> 00:14:46,485
I want to tell you the truth too.

236
00:14:46,885 --> 00:14:48,245
You're the best to play the Beast.

237
00:14:48,325 --> 00:14:49,805
Who are you calling the Beast?

238
00:14:49,885 --> 00:14:52,285
Look, your temper is much worse
than a beast.

239
00:14:52,365 --> 00:14:56,125
Situ Feng, do you want me to send you
flying in the air with my spinning kick?

240
00:14:56,205 --> 00:14:57,605
You dare?

241
00:14:58,165 --> 00:14:59,125
Knock it off.

242
00:14:59,525 --> 00:15:00,645
You're Belle

243
00:15:00,725 --> 00:15:01,885
and you're the Beast.

244
00:15:01,965 --> 00:15:04,285
-That'd be perfect.
-No!

245
00:15:04,365 --> 00:15:05,885
At least, I gained something.

246
00:15:08,725 --> 00:15:11,125
You both seem well-coordinated
when you were arguing.

247
00:15:11,205 --> 00:15:14,685
So it'd be nice
for you to take these roles.

248
00:15:14,765 --> 00:15:15,605
But Ms. Chen--

249
00:15:15,685 --> 00:15:16,645
How about this?

250
00:15:16,725 --> 00:15:18,125
Let's call a vote!

251
00:15:18,205 --> 00:15:20,285
Hands up if you don't want Situ Feng
to play Belle!

252
00:15:21,445 --> 00:15:22,445
Wait!

253
00:15:22,525 --> 00:15:23,565
This is not fair.

254
00:15:23,765 --> 00:15:24,845
No one put their hands up.

255
00:15:25,805 --> 00:15:26,685
All right.

256
00:15:28,325 --> 00:15:29,325
I've decided.

257
00:15:29,405 --> 00:15:30,885
Qingqing will be the Beast

258
00:15:30,965 --> 00:15:31,965
and Situ Feng,

259
00:15:32,845 --> 00:15:33,805
you'll play Belle.

260
00:15:35,365 --> 00:15:36,365
Hey, beauty.

261
00:15:37,685 --> 00:15:38,725
As for Lumière,

262
00:15:39,365 --> 00:15:41,725
Xinya will take the role.

263
00:15:41,805 --> 00:15:42,685
Beauty.

264
00:15:42,765 --> 00:15:43,805
Ms. Chen,

265
00:15:43,885 --> 00:15:46,805
if we give Xinya a supporting role,
she won't accept it.

266
00:15:46,885 --> 00:15:48,045
Ms. Chen,

267
00:15:48,125 --> 00:15:50,925
Xinya doesn't think highly
of such petty roles.

268
00:15:51,005 --> 00:15:52,645
How about you cast her as Gaston?

269
00:15:53,365 --> 00:15:54,645
It's a lead role too.

270
00:15:54,725 --> 00:15:55,725
Perhaps.

271
00:15:57,805 --> 00:15:58,725
Sorry.

272
00:15:58,925 --> 00:16:00,805
I was a little engrossed by it.

273
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:02,645
How did I do? A little better?

274
